## 9. Registry & Auth

```bash
docker login                          # Login to Docker Hub
docker login <registry-url>           # Login to private registry (ECR, GCR, GHCR)
docker logout
docker tag myapp:latest username/myapp:1.0
docker push username/myapp:1.0
docker pull username/myapp:1.0
```

